Citation.sAbstract: Isobaric vapor liquid equilibria were measured for three binary systems of water + propyleneglycol monomethyl ether (PGME),  water + propyleneglycol monomethyl ether acetate (PGMEA), and PGME+PGMEA at 93.3, 53.3, 26.7 kPa. The equipment used was a modified  Rogalski-Malanoski equilibrium still and an ebulliometer. The NRTL equation correlated the experimental binary data with good accuracy.
Citation.sTitle: Isobaric vapor liquid equilibria for water + propylene glycol monomethyl ether (PGME), water + propyleneglycol monomethyl ether acetate (PGMEA), and PGME+PGMEA at reduced pressures
